Uses of Class
org.spdx.library.model.v2.SpdxElement

  • Packages that use SpdxElement 
    Package Description
    org.spdx.library.model.v2
    Model compatible with version 2 of the SPDX spec (2.0, 2.1, 2.2, and 2.3)
    org.spdx.library.model.v2.pointer
    RDF model classes which implement the proposed W3C Pointer classes From the W3C documentation, pointers are entities that permit identifying a portion or segment of a piece of content - making use of the Resource Description Framework (RDF).

      A File represents a named sequence of information that is contained in a software package.
